{
  "texts": [
    "By combining these datasets, we create a practical and representative experimental dataset.",
    "Detailed statistics of this final dataset are presented in Table I.",
    "Experimental SettingsWe consider the following disinformation detection methods as baselines for comparison with DELD:• LLaMA: We use the pre-trained LLaMA2-7B to detect disinformation zero-shot.",
    "• ChatGPT: ChatGPT (GPT-4-turbo) from OpenAI is utilized to detect disinformation zero-shot.",
    "• FT-All: Fine-tuning a model on all data.• FT-Per: Fine-tuning a separate model per dataset.• FT-Seq: Fine-tuning a model on a sequence of datasets."
  ]
}